        <updateDate>2011-11-29T22:51:11Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Solar Jobs Creation Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) allow for periods ending before January 1, 2017, a 30% energy tax credit for equipment used to fabricate solar energy property; and (2) allow the energy tax credit for property that uses solar energy to heat swimming pools not located at single-family residences. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
